1. Doctor of Medicine degree from an ACGME accredited medical college.
2. Board certified, board eligible in required specialty (Family Medicine or Internal Medicine), or a current resident (subject to the requirements of the GME Moonlighting Policy: http://tigger.uic.edu/com/gme/p_p_moonlighting.htm)
3. Unrestricted Illinois license to practice medicine or Illinois license eligible.
